messageBody:
> Hi Can anyone let me know if JUnit 3.8.1 is compatible with JDK
> 1.4.2 . We are upgrading our boxes to JDK 1.4.2 and we would like to
> know that if JUnit 3.8.1 supports it and is there any know
> problem/bug for this upgrade.

It is compatible. No problems so far using it for the past
several months on various flavors of Windows...

Thanks, Derek
